00:20:23.291 --> 00:20:24.708
вҖӘHow are you doing?

393
00:20:24.791 --> 00:20:27.166
вҖӘ-We're good.
вҖӘ-Uh-huh. [sniffs]

394
00:20:27.250 --> 00:20:29.250
вҖӘ-Hmm. Did you cook?
вҖӘ-Mmm.

395
00:20:29.333 --> 00:20:31.583
вҖӘ-Keep it down. You shouldn't be here.
вҖӘ-[Matipa] Shut up. Shut up.

396
00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:33.958
вҖӘ-You always make a noise when you come.
вҖӘ-[Matipa] Joyce!

397
00:20:34.041 --> 00:20:35.375
вҖӘ-Please calm down.
вҖӘ-Are you done?

398
00:20:35.875 --> 00:20:37.375
вҖӘ-Joyce!
вҖӘ-[Ntombi] Oh. my goodness.

399
00:20:37.458 --> 00:20:40.166
вҖӘ-Ma'am. I tried to calm her down.
вҖӘ-No. don't worry about it.

400
00:20:40.250 --> 00:20:41.333
вҖӘ-Don't worry.
вҖӘ-[Ntombi] Oh. gosh.

401
00:20:41.416 --> 00:20:42.833
вҖӘ[Joyce] I know how to deal with trash.

402
00:20:42.916 --> 00:20:43.916
вҖӘHey. hey. hey. hey. hey.

403
00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:47.291
вҖӘWhat is your problem? Why do you always
вҖӘmake a lot of noise in my house?

404
00:20:47.375 --> 00:20:50.208
вҖӘAw. Joycie. I thought we're family now.

405
00:20:50.291 --> 00:20:53.375
вҖӘWhat's mine is yours
вҖӘand what's yours is mine.

406
00:20:53.458 --> 00:20:54.916
вҖӘ[Joyce scoffs]

407
00:20:55.000 --> 00:20:56.625
вҖӘWhat do you want. Matipa?

408
00:20:57.625 --> 00:20:59.375
вҖӘI'm looking for our husband.

409
00:21:01.333 --> 00:21:03.291
вҖӘHis children needed him today.

410
00:21:04.416 --> 00:21:08.208
вҖӘ-But he decided to be a no-show.
вҖӘ-Huh?

411
00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:10.000
вҖӘ[chuckles]

412
00:21:10.541 --> 00:21:12.458
вҖӘAre things falling apart for you?

413
00:21:12.541 --> 00:21:17.416
вҖӘ[chuckling] Oh. wow.
вҖӘthere's trouble in paradise.

414
00:21:18.083 --> 00:21:19.958
вҖӘSo tell me. dear.

415
00:21:20.041 --> 00:21:24.375
вҖӘby telling the first wife
вҖӘabout this dilemma of yours.

416
00:21:24.458 --> 00:21:26.666
вҖӘtell me what do you
вҖӘwant me to do about it?

417
00:21:26.750 --> 00:21:27.750
вҖӘHmm?

418
00:21:27.833 --> 00:21:29.916
вҖӘ-You just love putting on a show.
вҖӘ-[chuckling]

419
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.250
вҖӘ-I see that.
вҖӘ-[chuckling]

420
00:21:31.333 --> 00:21:34.000
вҖӘ-Let me tell you something. first wife.
вҖӘ-Mm-hmm.

421
00:21:35.250 --> 00:21:38.625
вҖӘYou forget that I know
вҖӘwhat type of woman you are.

422
00:21:39.208 --> 00:21:41.291
вҖӘYou're the blackmailing type.

423
00:21:41.375 --> 00:21:43.500
вҖӘ-Oh. okay.
вҖӘ-So maybe that's exactly what you did.

424
00:21:43.583 --> 00:21:44.708
вҖӘOh?

425
00:21:44.791 --> 00:21:47.083
вҖӘYou blackmailed him to stay with you.

426
00:21:47.166 --> 00:21:51.208
вҖӘ-Oh?
вҖӘ-You hate the fact that Jonasi chose me.

427
00:21:51.291 --> 00:21:53.750
вҖӘHe chose you? You're the chosen one?

428
00:21:53.833 --> 00:21:56.875
вҖӘ-My goodness. Forgive me. chosen one.
вҖӘ-[sighs]

429
00:21:56.958 --> 00:22:01.041
вҖӘPlease do me a favor.
вҖӘOpen your eyes and stop being an idiot.

430
00:22:01.791 --> 00:22:04.083
вҖӘDo you see your husband here? Huh?

431
00:22:04.166 --> 00:22:07.333
вҖӘIs Jonasi in this house?
вҖӘOr maybe you put him on my head?

432
00:22:07.416 --> 00:22:09.250
вҖӘDon't come here with that nonsense.

433
00:22:09.333 --> 00:22:11.375
вҖӘAnd do me one more favor. Matipa.

434
00:22:11.458 --> 00:22:15.000
вҖӘWhen you find that man of yours.
вҖӘlet him know I'm also looking for him.

435
00:22:15.083 --> 00:22:16.958
вҖӘHe needs to explain where he was today.

436
00:22:17.041 --> 00:22:19.666
вҖӘBecause he was meant to be
вҖӘat Nkazi's recital.

437
00:22:19.750 --> 00:22:21.875
вҖӘSomething I told him about months ago!

438
00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:26.583
вҖӘ[exhales sharply]

439
00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:30.166
вҖӘ[Essie] So. how are things?

440
00:22:31.750 --> 00:22:33.416
вҖӘIs the new wife treating you well?

441
00:22:33.500 --> 00:22:35.750
вҖӘ-[sighs]
вҖӘ-Is it that bad?

442
00:22:35.833 --> 00:22:38.750
вҖӘI don't know where to start. [scoffs] Wow.

443
00:22:39.291 --> 00:22:40.833
вҖӘ-[Essie scoffs]
вҖӘ-Mmm.

444
00:22:41.333 --> 00:22:42.625
вҖӘMmm!

445
00:22:42.708 --> 00:22:44.916
вҖӘ-Wow. My goodness.
вҖӘ-Jonasi.

446
00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:46.291
вҖӘ-It's delicious.
вҖӘ-[chuckles]

447
00:22:46.375 --> 00:22:48.125
вҖӘ-Mmm. Mmm.
вҖӘ-Is this how you eat now?

448
00:22:48.208 --> 00:22:49.208
вҖӘI'm hungry.

449
00:22:49.291 --> 00:22:50.666
вҖӘ-Wow.
вҖӘ-[Jonasi] Mmm.

450
00:22:50.750 --> 00:22:53.583
вҖӘWhy are you eating like a homeless person
вҖӘwhile you have a new wife?

451
00:22:53.666 --> 00:22:56.208
вҖӘ-Don't they cook at home?
вҖӘ-[chuckling]

452
00:22:56.291 --> 00:22:57.666
вҖӘ[Essie chuckles] Goodness.

453
00:22:57.750 --> 00:22:59.041
вҖӘI was really hungry.

454
00:22:59.625 --> 00:23:01.708
вҖӘOh. Please put it away.

455
00:23:01.791 --> 00:23:03.416
вҖӘ[Matipa] So you're telling meвҖҰ

456
00:23:04.916 --> 00:23:06.750
вҖӘhe disappeared on the both of us?

457
00:23:07.250 --> 00:23:08.541
вҖӘ[dramatic music playing]

458
00:23:10.291 --> 00:23:11.708
вҖӘLooks like it.

459
00:23:25.166 --> 00:23:26.333
вҖӘThis guy is here?

460
00:23:28.666 --> 00:23:31.166
вҖӘ[both breathing heavily]

461
00:23:31.250 --> 00:23:34.166
вҖӘ-Yes. [grunts] Yes.
вҖӘ-[moaning]
